snippet.title: mathtalk- analytic geometry intro
snippet.description:
intro to analytic geometry
Please note that at 6:15 I have accidentally used the reciprocal of the slopes of PA and AQ to develop the equation of a line. Good news though - it does not affect the end result as the same cross product is produced in the subsequent step. My apologies for any confusion that this may have caused. Happy Mathing!
